@startuml UC-EMP-02: View Active Projects

actor "Employee" as Emp
participant "Frontend" as FE
participant "ProjectController" as API
participant "ProjectService" as Svc
database "projects / project_members" as DB

Emp -> FE: Chọn "Dự án"
FE -> API: GET /api/v1/projects?status=ACTIVE&member=me
API -> Svc: getActiveProjectsByMember(currentUser.id)
Svc -> DB: findByMemberIdAndStatus(userId, ACTIVE)
DB --> Svc: List<Project>
Svc --> API: List<Project>
API --> FE: 200 List<Project>
FE --> Emp: Hiển thị DS dự án\n(tên, mã, Phase, NS khả dụng)

Emp -> FE: Chọn 1 DA → Xem chi tiết
FE -> API: GET /api/v1/projects/{id}
API -> Svc: getProjectById(projectId)
Svc -> DB: findById(projectId)
DB --> Svc: Project + phases + members
Svc --> API: Project
API --> FE: 200 Project
FE --> Emp: Hiển thị Phase, thành viên, Category budget

@enduml
